<br>
Find the Plane of Tranquility portal, and turn to face west.<br>
<br>
You will see the Soulbinder Soulbinder Jera.<br>
<br>
If you walk in a straight line between the PoT portal and the Soulbinder, you will pass a building on your right.  Enter it from the west side.  Open the first door that you see inside on the left, and you will find Seer Mal Nae'Shi sitting there (approx. NEG 42 NEG 214).<br>
<br>
Target the Seer, sit down, and /say guide meditation<br>
<br>
You must be sitting or she will ask you to sit and try agian.<br>
<br>
Once you do this successfully, you will see one line of hint text per quest flag that you have currently on you.<br>
<br>
